<p>Courtesy of Neal Parikh, to change the file format of the screen capture images, type:</p>
<blockquote><p><nobreak>defaults write com.apple.screencapture type _image-format_</nobreak></p></blockquote>
<p>where <em>image-format</em> is jpg, tiff, png, pdf, and maybe more!</p>
